          Tralee Golf Club is a legendary links golf course designed by Arnold Palmer with unprecedented views of the Atlantic Ocean
          In October 2009, Tralee Golf Club celebrated its 25th anniversary since its move from the town of Tralee
           to its present location on the edge of the Atlantic Ocean at West Barrow, Co. Kerry.
        </p>
