          Considered one of the finest links courses in the world, Ballybunion's reputation grew over time.
           Unfortunately, its remote locale on the Irish southwest coast has prevented the course from being selected for many top championship events.
           Still, a number of the world's best players have found their way to the famed course.
        </p>
